\v 2 EseZiyoni, ukuphelela kobuhle\x + Lilo 2.15. Hlab. 48.2.\x*, uNkulunkulu ukhanyile\x + Dute. 33.2. Jobe 3.4. 10.3,22. Hlab. 80.1. 94.1.\x*.
\v 3 UNkulunkulu wethu uzakuza, kayikuthula; umlilo phambi kwakhe uzaqothula, enhlangothini zonke zakhe kuzakuba lesiphepho esikhulu\x + Hlab. 21.9. Levi 10.2.\x*.
\v 4 Uzabiza amazulu ephezulu, lomhlaba, ukwahlulela abantu bakhe\x + Dute. 4.26.\x*.
