\v 6 Lamazulu azatshumayela ukulunga kwakhe\x + Hlab. 97.6. Hlab. 19.1. 89.5.\x*, ngoba uNkulunkulu ngokwakhe ungumahluleli. \w Sela\w**\x + Hlab. 75.7. Hlab. 58.11.\x*.
\v 7 Zwanini bantu bami, ngizakhuluma\x + Hlab. 81.8.\x*; Israyeli, ngizafakaza ngimelene lawe\x + Hlab. 81.8.\x*. NginguNkulunkulu, uNkulunkulu wakho\x + Eks. 20.2.\x*.
\v 8 Kangikusoli ngenxa yemihlatshelo yakho\x + Jer. 7.22. Hlab. 51.16. 1 Sam. 15.22.\x*; leminikelo yakho yokutshiswa ihlala iphambi kwami\x + Hlab. 51.3.\x*.
\v 9 Kangiyikuthatha ijongosi elivela emzini wakho\x + Seb. 17.25. Hlab. 16.2.\x*, \add l\add*ezimpongo ezivela ezibayeni zakho\x + Hlab. 78.70. Hab. 3.17.\x*.
\v 10 Ngoba ngeyami yonke inyamazana yehlathi, izinkomo ezisentabeni eziyizinkulungwane.
\v 11 Ngiyazazi izinyoni zonke zezintaba, lezilo zommango zikimi\x + Hlab. 80.13. Isa. 66.11.\x*.
\v 12 Uba bengilambile, bengingayikukutshela, ngoba umhlaba ngowami lokugcwala kwawo\x + Hlab. 24.1.\x*.
\v 13 Ngizayidla yini inyama yezinkunzi\x + Hlab. 22.12.\x*, kumbe nginathe igazi lezimpongo?
\v 14 Nikela kuNkulunkulu\x + 50.23. Hlab. 69.30,31. Hos. 14.2. Heb. 13.15. Hlab. 27.6. Roma 12.1.\x* umhlatshelo wokubonga\x + 2 Lan. 29.31. 33.16. Hlab. 56.12. Hlab. 100. Heb. 13.15. Hlab. 69.30. 107.22.\x*, ukhokhe izithembiso zakho koPhezukonke\x + Jobe 22.27. Hlab. 61.8. 65.1. Zaga 7.14. Nani 30.2. Hlab. 22.25.\x*.
\v 15 Ungibize osukwini lokuhlupheka\x + Hlab. 81.7. Hlab. 77.2. Zek. 13.9. Hlab. 107.6.\x*, ngizakukhulula\x + Hlab. 91.15.\x*, ubusungidumisa\x + 50.23. Hlab. 22.23.\x*.
