\v 19 Umlomo wakho uyawunikela ebubini, lolimi lwakho luqambe inkohliso\x + Hlab. 52.2.\x*.
\v 20 Uhlala ukhulume umelene lomfowenu, uhlebe indodana kanyoko\x + Jobe 19.18.\x*.
\v 21 Lezizinto uzenzile, ngathula\x + Isa. 57.11. Tshu. 8.11.\x*; wacabanga ukuthi nginjengawe kanye\x + Roma 2.4.\x*. Ngizakukhuza\x + 2 Kho. 19.4. Hlab. 90.8.\x*, ngikuhlele phambi kwamehlo akho\x + Jobe 13.18. 23.4. Hlab. 5.3.\x*.
\v 22 Kuqapheleni-ke lokhu, lina elikhohlwa uNkulunkulu\x + Hlab. 9.17.\x*, hlezi ngi\add li\add*dabule, kungabi khona okukhululayo\x + Hlab. 7.2.\x*.
\v 23 Onikela umnikelo wokubonga\x + 50.14.\x* uyangidumisa\x + 50.23. Hlab. 22.23.\x*; lolungisa indlela \add yakhe\add* ngizambonisa usindiso lukaNkulunkulu.
